%p.bigger.bold The BipolarType Energy Cycle
%table
  %tbody
    %tr
      %th ↗️
      %th 😳
      %th ↘️
    %tr
      %th 😃
      %th 🔁
      %th 😌
    %tr
      %th ↖️
      %th 😞
      %th ↙️
%ul.none
  %li 😃 Productive: use energy
  %li 😳 Manic: waste energy
  %li 😌 Receptive: get energy
  %li 😞 Depressed: hoard energy
%p The goal of BipolarType is to minimize the time you spend in 😳 and 😞 and maximize the time you spend in 😃 and 😌.

.bigger.bold The BipolarType Realms
%ul.none
  =list_of Realm.each do |realm|
    %ul.none
      %li #{realm.symbol} #{realm.name}: Get and use #{realm.energy}
      %li.indented Get #{realm.energy}: #{realm.get} and #{realm.consume}
      %li.indented Use #{realm.energy}: #{realm.use2} (#{realm.use})
%p BipolarType tries to maximize #{Realm.names.map(&:downcase).and} health by focusing on the solution instead of the problem.
